title: LiveLeak.com - Lava "fire hose" gushes into the Pacific Ocean
text:
Lava "fire hose" gushes into the Pacific Ocean Part of channel(s): Liveleakers (promoted) 
Yesterday I flew my Phantom 3 out at Kalapana to see the "61G" lava ocean entry. About a month ago a section of cliff broke off into the ocean and exposed a lava tube feeding the flow, which has been dubbed the "lava fire hose". https://hvo.wr.usgs.gov/activity/kilaueastatus.php
